data.description: Better price for a 5 Acre property you can soon call home.  Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own your own piece of paradise.  Welcome to this picturesque single-family home situated on a serene 5-acre property, offering a harmonious blend of rural living and modern comfort. The moment you arrive and approach the front porch adorned with rose bushes, you'll be greeted by breathtaking views of the Appalachian foothills that stretch as far as the eye can see, creating an ever-changing masterpiece with the seasons. Step inside to discover a 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence that seamlessly combines modern comfort with a welcoming atmosphere, featuring hardwood floors throughout the main level living spaces.  Upon entry, you'll encounter a cozy foyer with a wood-burning stove, setting the tone for intimate gatherings and warm evenings. The living areas are versatile and inviting, including both a living room and a family room adorned with elegant French doors, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Ample closets ensure organized living.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring an enormous eat-in area with abundant natural light from skylights and windows above the double sink. Equipped with an island, bar seating, and ample cabinets, it offers functionality and style. A planning area complements this spacious kitchen, complete with modern appliances, Corian countertops, and a well-lit cooking space. The kitchen seamlessly connects to a rear deck through a sliding door, ideal for outdoor dining and entertaining.  The large laundry room cleverly conceals a washer and dryer behind a barn door, providing both functionality and elegance. A versatile office/study with built-in shelving and a ceiling fan can easily transition into a 4th bedroom to suit your evolving needs. Three additional bedrooms include the primary bedroom, a true retreat with a comfortable sitting area and an updated primary bathroom featuring double sinks and modern black hardware.  This home offers plenty of storage and two additional full bathrooms. A newly re-roofed 3-stall barn with a tack room awaits your equine companions, and the subdivided and Ramm-fenced pasture offers ample space for them to graze and roam freely. The backyard is a true outdoor oasis with a wood deck and fire pit, perfect for gatherings, stargazing, and enjoying the serene surroundings. Versatile outbuildings, including a fenced area with a greenhouse, provide additional opportunities.  This home has received significant updates, including a new roof in 2019, a dehumidifier-equipped crawlspace in 2020, and a brand new HVAC system in 2022, ensuring year-round comfort. The oversized 2-car detached garage with shelving and circular driveway adds convenience to this property.  While this property exudes a farm-like ambiance, it's only a short 5-minute drive to the shopping and amenities of Warrenton, offering the best of both worlds. Nature lovers will appreciate the proximity to hiking and hunting areas, as well as the majestic mountains for exploration. This property provides a sanctuary where you can enjoy outdoor activities and pets have space to roam.  Escape the hustle and bustle of Northern Virginia and embrace a lifestyle that balances tranquility with convenience. This property is more than a home; it's a haven of natural beauty, a place to create cherished memories, and an everyday retreat. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream property your forever home. Owner will be conveying a newer snow blower and other farm supplies such as  some fencing,  smaller troughs , electric fencing supplies, some drainage materials,  and some extra wood.  For the new owner with a green thumb the wonderful greenhouse will convey also.
